channel.title: Requesting a logo for "LoadedPk"
channel.description:
I would like for someone to make me a logo for a website. Its going to be sleek, simple, but still tie into the RS2 feel. There is no specfic size for this. The background will be transparent and the text will be "LoadedPk" with a silver with a drop shadow.
Ex: [img]https://encrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS3NEALmCRVzTwN3n2DTXgzaT6BpqYtJJBwEE56Xvv8k8lh_cqGYA[/img]
This is the look that i wanted but in silver so somthing around that font would be nice Thank you if you consider making it! Skype: jehe35
